EASY STORAGE, THANKS TO THE ON-BOARD HOSE AND STEAM PLATE STORAGE.  SUPPLIED WITH A LARGE STEAM PLATE THAT COVERS A WIDE AREA AND SAVES TIME. name: MT 300KA OSCILLATING TOOL 300W 240V
description: THE BLACK AND DECKER MT300KA OSCILLATING TOOL FEATURES A SUPERLOK™ TOOL-FREE ACCESSORY CHANGE SYSTEM FOR FASTER JOB COMPLETION. IT HAS A ROBUST JAM POT DESIGN, WHICH PROVIDES DURABILITY AND EASY SERVICING. THE SLIM BACK HANDLE DESIGN AND SOFT GRIP PROVIDES GREATER COMFORT FOR LONGER USE. THE VARIABLE SPEED PROVIDES OPTIMUM CONTROL ON ALL TASKS.  THE OSCILATING TOOL HAS A SANDING PLATEN WHICH INCLUDES INTEGRATED DUST EXTRACTION FOR A CLEANER WORKING ENVIRONMENT. THE TOOLED ACCESSORY ADAPTOR PROVIDES ADDITIONAL VERSATILITY TO FIT BOSCH, EINHELL AND WORX ACCESSORIES IN A TOOLED MANNER.  APPLICATIONS: A MULTITUDE OF FINISHING TASKS, INCLUDING CUTTING, SANDING, REMOVAL AND SCRAPING. CUTTING WOOD, METAL, PLASTERBOARD, LAMINATE FLOORING, PLASTICS AND FIBERGLASS. SANDING WOODS, LAMINATE FLOORING, STONE, BREEZEBLOCKS, PLASTERBOARD AND FOR POLISHING AND RUST REMOVAL. SCRAPING LINOLEUM FLOORING TILE ADHESIVE, CERAMIC TILE ADHESIVE, REMOVAL OF LINOLEUM, CARPET TILES AND SEALANT REMOVAL.  COMES WITH:  1 X SANDING PAD WITH INTEGRATED DUST EXTRACTION. 1 X PRECISION PLUNGE CUT BLADE. 1 X SEGMENTED FLUSH CUT BLADE. 1 X RIGID SCRAPER BLADE. 1 X FLEXIBLE SCRAPER BLADE. 6 X SANDING SHEETS 60, 80 AND 120 GRIT1 X TOOLED ACCESSORY ADAPTER TO FIT BOSCH, EINHELL AND WORX TOOLED ACCESSORIES.  SPECIFICATION  INPUT POWER: 300 WATT.NO LOAD SPEED: 10,000-22,000/MIN.CABLE LENGTH: 3M.WEIGHT: 1.58KG.

name: PD1820LF DUSTBUSTER FLEXI HAND VAC & FLOOR EXTENSION KIT 25W 18V
description: THE BLACK AND DECKER PD1820LF DUSTBUSTER® FLEXI HAND VAC USES 18 VOLT LITHIUM-ION BATTERY TECHNOLOGY FOR STRONG SUCTION AND FADE FREE POWER. IT IS A HIGH PERFORMANCE CORDLESS HAND VAC WITH INTEGRATED 1.5M FLEXIBLE HOSE, HELPING YOU TO CLEAN THOSE HARD TO REACH, AWKWARD SPACES. IT HAS A CYCLONIC ACTION AND TRIPLE ACTION FILTRATION ALLOWS THE PRODUCT TO PERFORM BETTER AND LAST LONGER.  THE ECO SMART CHARGE IN UNDER 4 HOURS AND THE CHARGER AUTOMATICALLY TURNS OFF ONCE THE UNIT IS FULLY CHARGED, SAVING ELECTRICITY. THE VAC IS FITTED WITH A CHARGE INDICATOR LIGHT THAT FLASHES 30 SECONDS BEFORE THE BATTERY CHARGE RUNS OUT. IT IS FITTED WITH A HIGH PERFORMANCE MOTOR FOR MAXIMUM CLEANING PERFORMANCE AND IS IDEAL FOR THE MORE DEMANDING CLEAN-UP TASKS.  IT IS FITTED WITH A FULLY REMOVABLE TRANSLUCENT BOWL FOR EASY AND HYGIENIC CLEANING AND A QUICK AND EASY EMPTY FEATURE, SIMPLY OPEN THE SIDE DOOR AND EMPTY THE DEBRIS INTO YOUR BIN. IT HAS A PATENTED 'MOTOR IN THE FILTER' DESIGN AND LITHIUM BATTERY TECHNOLOGY PROVIDE A COMPACT AND LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN WITH NO COMPROMISE ON POWER.  THIS MODEL IS SUPPLIED WITH THE FLOOR EXTENSION KIT WHICH ALLOWS YOU TO CLEAN HARD FLOOR AND SMALL CARPETED AREAS WITH THE EASY TO STEER FLOOR KIT. INCLUDES LONG AND SHORT CREVICE TOOLS AND SOFT BRUSH FOR CLEANING VERSATILITY AND THE CHARGING DOCKING STATION STORES UNIT AND ACCESSORIES.  SPECIFICATION  INPUT POWER: 25 WATT. SUCTION PRESSURE: 541MM/WATER. AIR FLOW: 1062L/MIN. DUSTBOWL CAPACITY: 560ML. RUNTIME: 15MIN. FIRST TIME CHARGE: 4 HOURS.

name: SVJ520BFS CORDLESS 2-IN-1 DUSTBUSTER 36W 18V
description: THE BLACK & DECKER SVJ520BFS CORDLESS 2-IN-1 DUSTBUSTER® CAN BE USED AS A FLOOR AND A HANDHELD VACUUM, ALLOWING YOU TO CLEAN ANY SURFACE AROUND THE HOME. WITH SMART TECH SENSOR TECHNOLOGY THAT DETECTS WHEN THE FILTER BECOMES CLOGGED AND NEEDS TO BE CLEANED, HELPING TO MAINTAIN CLEANING PERFORMANCE. THE INTELLIGENT FLOOR SENSOR INCREASES SUCTION ON DEEP PILE CARPETS AND SWITCHES TO ECO MODE FOR LIGHTER TASKS, EXTENDING BATTERY RUN TIME. THE SMART TECH BATTERY SENSOR DISPLAYS THE REMAINING BATTERY CHARGE, SO YOU&RSQUO;RE NOT CAUGHT SHORT OF POWER WHILST CLEANING.  UTILISING A CYCLONIC ACTION TO SPIN DUST AND DEBRIS AWAY FROM THE FILTER SO SUCTION POWER REMAINS STRONG. INTELLIGENT BOOST MODE ALLOWS THE SUCTION POWER TO BE INCREASED FOR TOUGH DEBRIS. TRIPLE ACTION FILTRATION PROVIDES GREAT LONG LASTING PERFORMANCE. THE SLIM NOZZLE PROVIDES GREATER ACCESSIBILITY AND EXTRA CONVENIENCE AND THE WIDE MOUTH DESIGN MEANS THIS VAC CAN EFFORTLESSLY SCOOP UP LARGE DEBRIS. THE TRANSLUCENT, BAGLESS DIRT BOWL MAKES IT EASY TO SEE THE DIRT AND EMPTY.  USES SMART CHARGE TECHNOLOGY TO CHARGE THE BATTERY WITHIN 5 HOURS. THE BASE CHARGER PROVIDES EASY AND CONVENIENT CHARGING.  SUPPLIED WITH: 1 X BASE CHARGER, 1 X ON BOARD CREVICE TOOL AND 1 X PUSH-IN BRUSH.  SPECIFICATION  INPUT POWER: 36 WATT.SUCTION POWER: 25 AIR WATTS, HANDHELD: 40MM/WATER.AIR FLOW: 826/984 L/MIN.DUSTBOWL CAPACITY: 500ML.RUN TIME: 14-20 MINS.CHARGE TIME: 5 HOURS.

name: BAHCO STILLSON TYPE PIPE WRENCH
description:
Bahco Professional Stillson Type Pipe Wrench forged from high quality steel. Both jaws have deep grooves ensuring instant grip and ratcheting action.

Can be used with copper, aluminium, ferrous and non-ferrous metals.

name: BAHCO VIP BI-METAL VARIABLE PITCH HOLESAW
description:
Bahco Sandflex Variable Pitch Holesaw made for high precision cutting of holes from 14mm to 152mm diameter in all sawable materials up to 29mm thick.

Suitable for use in portable electric or pneumatic tools, and in a wide variety of drilling, boring, milling and other machine tools.

Cutting edges are in high speed steel for extra hardness, with welded seams for accuracy of cut, and heat-treated bodies for maximum strength. All saws have varipitch (4-6tpi) blades.

Supplied in cardboard box.

name: BAHCO SUPERIOR MULTI CONSTRUCTION HOLESAW
description:
Bahco Superior Multi Construction Holesaws have carbide tips and are capable of cutting through brick and ceramic tiles, laminate, fibreglass and hardwood. The tooth tips consist of a carbide round rod which is fusion welded to the back material, the tip is then ground to its final shape with a 5 DEGREE positive cutting angle.

They have a low friction coating that minimises heat generation and wide gullets for effective chip removal.

They fit all power drills, both stationary and portable

name: PLUMBER'S BI-METAL HOLESAW SET, 14 PIECE
description: THE BAHCO PLUMBER'S BI-METAL HOLESAW SET CONTAINS SANDFLEX® BI-METAL HOLESAWS, SPECIALLY DESIGNED FOR METAL CUTTING: FERROUS METALS (STEEL, STAINLESS STEEL, CAST IRON) AND NON-FERROUS METALS (ALUMINIUM, BRASS, COPPER). THEY CAN ALSO BE USED IN MOST MATERIALS SUCH AS WOOD AND PLASTICS. BI-METAL CONSTRUCTION WITH 8% COBALT FOR INCREASED WEAR RESISTANCE.  THIS 14 PIECE KIT CONTAINS:   12 X HOLESAWS: 16, 20(X2), 22, 25(X2), 29, 32, 35(X2), 38 AND 44MM2 X ARBORS

name: BAHCO COMBINATION AUGER BIT
description:
The Bahco 9626 Series Combination Auger Bits are made from hardened tool steel and lacquered for rust protection. Spirals with Levin pattern. Can be used in both electric power drills and hand braces. Part of the tang has a hexagonal shank (15mm long) for a firm grip in the chuck, suitable for hand braces.

The threaded tip moderates a self-feed when using a power drill, but still sufficient self-feed when used in a hand brace. Ideal for quick precision cutting with all types of wood.

This Bahco 9626 Series Combination Auger Bit has the following specification:

name: BAHCO LONG COMBINATION AUGER BIT
description:
The Bahco 9627 Series Long Combination Auger Bit is longer than a standard auger bit, designed for long-reach applications. Made from hardened tool steel, lacquered for rust protection. Spirals with Levin pattern. Can be used in both electric power drills and hand braces.

The threaded tip moderates a self-feed when using a power drill, but still sufficient self-feed when used in a hand brace. For quick precision cutting with all types of wood.

name: BESSEY LEVER CLAMPS
description:
Clamping with leverage Speed, safety and strength

The original BESSEY lever clamps are lightweight, easy to handle, dimensionally stable, and torsion resistant. And the best thing is: they can clamp up to 5x faster than conventional clamps. This is because they use the natural force of the lever, meaning that with just a small amount of effort they can quickly produce large clamping pressures. This is particularly valuable in situations where many clamps have to be applied in a short time, with no risk of loosening due to vibrations. Try it out!

The lever clamp GH allows you to clamp up to 5 x faster than with conventional clamps.

Rapid - Up to 5 x faster than conventional clamps
Secure - Unaffected by vibrations
Strong - High clamping force
Your benefits at a glance:

Secure ratchet mechanism
The ratchet mechanism ensures rapid, controlled, vibration free clamping. Hardened cam at the end of the lever ensures a long service life.

Extremely sturdy
Fixed bracket and pressure plate are produced and tempered from a single piece, thus very torsion-resistant. This guarantees you maximum tensile strength and sturdiness.

Forged sliding arm
The sliding arm is serrated and made from tempered, drop-forged steel. For an extremely long service life.

Ergonomically shaped clamping lever
The powder-coated clamping lever and the plastic-coated release lever are also remarkably ergonomic.

description: THE BOSTITCH C24-U PORTABLE COMPRESSOR IS A COMPACT AND PORTABLE UNIT. description:

IT HAS AN ULTRA-COMPACT, LIGHTWEIGHT DESIGN THAT MAKES IT PERFECT FOR USE IN CONFINED SPACES. THE 2-SPEED ALL-METAL TRANSMISSION PROVIDES INCREASED RUN TIME AND LONGER TOOL LIFE WITH DRILL DRIVER AND HAMMER FEATURES FOR MULTIPLE APPLICATIONS. name: DCF620D2K BRUSHLESS COLLATED DRYWALL SCREWDRIVER 18V 2 X 2.0AH LI-ION
description:
THE DEWALT DCF620D2K BRUSHLESS COLLATED DRYWALL SCREWDRIVER IS IDEAL FOR EFFICIENT FITTING OF DRYWALL. IT HAS A POWERFUL BRUSHLESS MOTOR THAT DRIVES SCREWS EFFICIENTLY AND EFFECTIVELY AND WHICH OFFERS MAXIMUM RUNTIME.  THIS DRYWALL SCREWDRIVER IS ONE OF THE LIGHTEST AND MOST COMPACT TOOLS ON THE MARKET MAKING IT IDEAL FOR USE IN TIGHT SPACES. ITS QUICK RELEASE COLLATED SCREW MAGAZINE ACCEPTS MOST COLLATED SCREWS TO ALLOW THE USER TO FIT BOARDS MORE QUICKLY. THE MAGAZINE ROTATES ON THE TOOL WITHOUT REMOVAL TO ALLOW USE IN CORNERS WITH MINIMUM FUSS.  THE DCF620D2K FEATURES TOOL FREE DEPTH CONTROL AND FINE DEPTH CONTROL FOR SIMPLE BUT EFFECTIVE SETTING. ITS LED WORKLIGHT OFFERS VALUABLE LIGHT WHEN WORKING IN SMALL SPACES OR AREAS WITH LIMITED LIGHT. A TRIGGER LOCK ALLOWS COMFORTABLE, PROLONGED WORK.  THE DCF620D2K HAS AN ERGONOMICALLY DESIGNED RUBBER GRIP FOR EXCELLENT USER COMFORT WHILST USING THE TOOL IN EITHER THE 'IN-LINE' OR 'PISTOL-GRIP' HAND POSITION. IT IS ALSO SUPPLIED WITH LOCKING NOSE CONE, ALLOWING WORK WITH THE SAME TOOL ON SITES WHERE COLLATED DRYWALL SCREWS ARE NOT SUPPLIED. THE 'SET AND FORGET' FEATURE REMEMBERS YOUR FINE DEPTH ADJUSTMENT SETTING WHEN REMOVING AND REPLACING THE NOSE CONE.  SUPPLIED WITH: 2 X 18 VOLT 2.0AH XR LI-ION BATTERIES, 1 X MULTI-VOLTAGE XR CHARGER, 1 X DCF6201 COLLATED SCREW MAGAZINE, 1 X DT7205-QZ PR2 COLLATED SCREW BIT, 1 X SINGLE SCREW NOSE CONE, 1 X DT7520-QZ MAGNETIC BIT EXTENDER WITH 25MM PR2 SCREW BIT AND 1 X TSTAK 2 KITBOX.  SPECIFICATION  BIT HOLDER: 6.35MM (1/4IN).NO LOAD 
SPEED: 0-4,400/MIN.TORQUE: 5-30NM.COLLATED HEAD CAPACITY: 55MM.WEIGHT: 1.88KG.

name: DT2440L 2X LIFE RECIPROCATING SAW BLADE 6 PIECE SET
description: THE DEWALT 2X LIFE RECIPROCATING SAW BLADE 6 PIECE SET CONTAINS A MIXTURE OF BLADE TYPES FOR A WIDE RANGE OF CUTTING JOBS AND IS SUPPLIED IN A HASSLE-FREE, RE-USABLE STORAGE CASE THAT QUICKLY AND EASILY ADJUSTS TO SUIT THE BLADE LENGTHS.  THEY HAVE SUPERIOR HSS (HIGH SPEED STEEL) TEETH WITH ADDED COBALT FOR HARDER, STRONGER TEETH WITH GREATER FLEX FOR EXCELLENT CUTTING PERFORMANCE AND LONG LIFE EVEN IN THE MOST DEMANDING APPLICATIONS. FAST AND ACCURATE CUTTING IN WOOD APPLICATIONS THANKS TO THE PLUNGE POINT TIP TECHNOLOGY WHICH PIERCES THE WOOD AND REMOVES MORE MATERIAL.  THEY HAVE AN OPTIMISED BLADE DESIGN OFFERING INCREASED HEIGHT AND THICKNESS FOR STURDINESS, STRENGTH AND EXTREME DURABILITY. THE TOUGHCOAT HARDENED COATING LOWERS SURFACE FRICTION AND REDUCES HEAT BUILD UP TO PROMOTE LONG BLADE LIFE. THEY HAVE AN AGGRESSIVE SHANK ANGLE THAT INCREASES TOOTH ENGAGEMENT IN ALL MATERIALS AND EXTENDS BLADE LIFE.  THE METAL BLADES HAVE AN OPTIMISED TOOTH DESIGN WITH A 14/18 TPI VARIABLE TOOTH GEOMETRY REDUCES TOOTH BREAKAGE IN HARD METALS FOR EXTREME DURABILITY EVEN IN THE MOST DEMANDING APPLICATIONS.  CONTAINS:  1 X DT2307L 2X LIFE WOOD & NAIL RECIPROCATING BLADE 228MM, 6 TPI.1 X DT2308L 2X LIFE GENERAL PURPOSE RECIPROCATING BLADE, 10 TPI.1 X DT2300L 2X LIFE WOOD & NAIL RECIPROCATING BLADE 152MM, 6 TPI.1 X DT2301L 2X LIFE GENERAL PURPOSE RECIPROCATING BLADE 152MM, 10 TPI.1 X DT2407L 2X LIFE METAL RECIPROCATING BLADE 152MM, 14/18 TPI.1 X DT2315L 2X LIFE GENERAL PURPOSE RECIPROCATING BLADE 100MM, 10 TPI.

name: DT70750 FLAT DRILL BIT SET, 8 PIECE
description: DEWALT FLAT DRILL BITS ARE MADE FROM HIGH-QUALITY CHROME VANADIUM STEEL WITH A GROUND CENTRAL POINT AND CUTTING EDGES FOR ACCURATE LOCATION AND CLEAN CUTTING. THEY ALSO HAVE A GROUND CHIP BREAKER TO REDUCE SPLINTERING PROVIDING RELATIVELY CLEAN HOLES AND IMPROVED DRILLING EFFICIENCY.  IDEAL FOR RAPID DRILLING OF HOLES IN WOOD. SUITABLE FOR NATURAL HARDWOOD AND SOFTWOOD, CHIPBOARD AND OTHER MAN-MADE MATERIALS.  SUPPLIED IN A TOUGH CASE+, THIS IS PART OF A CONNECTABLE CASE SYSTEM THAT IS TSTAK™ COMPATIBLE. name: DT70751 EXTREME FLAT BIT SET, 9 PIECE

THE PRECISION GROUND CENTRAL POINT HAS AN OPTIMISED DESIGN FOR FASTER MATERIAL PENETRATION AND INCREASED DRILLING SPEED.  IDEAL FOR THE RAPID DRILLING OF HOLES IN WOOD, FOR DOOR LOCKS, MORTISING, ELECTRICAL AND PLUMBING WORK. SUITABLE FOR NATURAL HARDWOOD AND SOFTWOOD, CHIPBOARD AND OTHER MAN-MADE MATERIALS. name: DEWALT BI-METAL DEEP CUT HOLESAW
description:
The DEWALT Bi-Metal 2X Life Holesaws are designed for heavy-duty cutting in standard or deep cut applications. They are fitted with a quick-release mandrel that prevents lock up of the holesaw and enables it to be easily removed.

The extra hard, variable pitch, high-speed steel teeth have an M3 steel cutting edge that provides extended holesaw life. They provide a 12.5mm deeper cut than standard bi-metal holesaws. Ideal for cutting holes in steel, stainless steel, brass, copper, aluminium, wood, plastic and other composition.

description: DEWALT EXTREME TRI-FLUTE SPADE BITS WITH 3 CUTTING EDGES FOR UP TO 6X FASTER CUTTING, COMBINED WITH A TRI-FLUTE FOR OPTIMUM CHIP REMOVAL AND LESS BINDING. THERE ARE 3 CUTTING SPURS FOR CLEANER AND FASTER HOLES, THE SPURS ALSO EXTEND DRILLING LIFE. ITS FULL SCREW TIP ALLOWS THE BIT TO SELF-FEED, FOR EASE OF USE AND PULL THROUGH. THIS 6 PIECE SET CONTAINS THE FOLLOWING SIZES: 13, 16, 20, 22, 25 AND 32MM.

name: CLEAN ROOM SILICONE C3 565
description: EVERBUILD CLEAN ROOM SILICONE IS AN ADVANCED NEUTRAL CURING HYGIENIC SEALANT THAT COMBINES MOULD SHIELD, A POWERFUL ANTI-BACTERIAL COMPOUND WITH FDA APPROVED FOOD COMPATIBILITY. IT PREVENTS THE FORMATION OF MOST COMMON GERMS ON ITS SURFACE INCLUDING E-COLI, MRSA, SALMONELLA, LISTERIA AND STAPHYLOCOCCUS AND STOPS BLACK MOULD GROWTH.  CLEAN ROOM SILICONE OFFERS OUTSTANDING ADHESION TO MOST SUBSTRATES INCLUDING PLASTICS, CERAMICS AND METAL. IT IS VIRTUALLY ODOURLESS IN APPLICATION WITH A SLOW SKINNING TIME, MAKING IT IDEAL FOR LONG JOINT RUNS IN LARGER APPLICATIONS. REMAINS PERMANENTLY FLEXIBLE WITH A MOVEMENT CAPABILITY OF &PLUSMN; 25%.  TESTED AND APPROVED TO FDA, US FOOD AND DRUG ADMINISTRATION REGULATION NO 21CFR177.2600 BY IANESCO (FRANCE).MEETS ISO 11600 F&G 25HM.

name: DUAL PURPOSE FOAM CLEANER 500ML
description: THE EVERBUILD EVBGFSC5 DUAL PURPOSE FOAM CLEANER IS USED TO REMOVE WET / UNCURED FOAM FROM BRICK, PVCU, PLASTER ETC. THIS EVBGFSC5 SIMPLY ATTACHES TO EVERBUILD GUN FOAM APPLICATOR FOR PURGING THROUGH, ALSO INCLUDES SPRAY NOZZLE FOR USE WITHOUT APPLICATOR TO REMOVE WET FOAM FROM OUTSIDE OF THE GUN AND FROM MOST BUILDING SUBSTRATES.  EASY TO USE WITH SOME SIMPLE STEPS: PULL THE TRIGGER ON THE GUN TO RELEASE THE SOLVENT INTO THE GUN BARREL AND DISCHARGE THE SOLVENT INTO A SUITABLE CONTAINER FOR DISPOSAL. ONLY STOP DISCHARGING THE CLEANER WHEN THE SOLUTION BEING EJECTED FROM THE GUN IS COMPLETELY CLEAR. LEAVE THE GUN FOAM CLEANSE ATTACHED TO THE GUN FOR 5 MINUTES TO ALLOW THE SOLVENT IN THE GUN TO WORK ON THE RESIDUES INSIDE. PULL THE TRIGGER ONCE AGAIN UNTIL ONLY CLEAR SOLVENT EMERGES. LEAVE FOR A FURTHER 5 MINUTES AND REPEAT THIS PROCESS 2 OR 3 TIMES UNTIL THE GUN IS COMPLETELY CLEAR.  500ML.

name: GRIPTITE CONSTRUCTION ADHESIVE C4 350ML
description:
EVERBUILD GRIPTITE IS A READY TO USE GAP FILLING AND PANEL ADHESIVE BASED ON A HIGH BOND STRENGTH SYNTHETIC RUBBER/RESIN MIX IN A SOLVENT CARRIER. ADHERES TO MOST COMMON SURFACES INSIDE AND OUTSIDE THE HOME. BONDS TO WOOD, PLASTER, PLASTERBOARD, CARPET, CARPET GRIPPERS, METAL, GLASS, CERAMICS, BRICK, CONCRETE, CORK, PVCU AND CERTAIN PLASTICS.  BENEFITS;SOLVENT BASED FORMULA - QUICK DRYING / HIGH EARLY BOND STRENGTH.EXCELLENT ADHESION/BOND STRENGTH - ADHERES TO MOST COMMON SURFACES.GOOD EARLY GRAB PROPERTIES - USABLE IN BOTH VERTICAL AND HORIZONTAL POSITIONS.HIGH SOLIDS FORMULATION - EXCELLENT GAP FILLING PROPERTIES WITHOUT SHRINKAGE.SUITABLE FOR USE WHERE BOTH SURFACES ARE NON-POROUS.EXCELLENT EXTERNAL WEATHERING PROPERTIES-SUITABLE FOR EXTERIOR USE  IDEAL FOR:BONDING DADO RAILS, ARCHITRAVES AND SKIRTING. FIXING PARQUET AND CORK FLOORING.FIXING WALL CLADDING DIRECT TO INTERNAL WALL SURFACES OR TIMBER BATTENS.FIXING BATTENS DIRECTLY ONTO WALLS WITHOUT FASTENINGS.BONDING CARPET GRIPPER SYSTEMS TO MOST FLOORS WITHOUT THE NEED FOR NAILS OR TACKS.BONDING STAIR NOSING TO CONCRETE OR WOODEN STAIRS.FIXING POLYESTER, WOOD, PVCU OR METAL THRESHOLDS.FIXING NAMEPLATES, PLASTIC BOXES, DECORATIVE FRAMES, WALL SOCKETS AND JUNCTION BOXES TO MOST SURFACES.SECURING ALUMINIUM OR OTHER SKIN PANELS TO THE FRAMEWORK OR PORTABLE INDUSTRIAL BUILDINGS AND CARAVANS.  LIMITATIONS;DO NOT USE ON DAMP SURFACES: USE EVERBUILD GUN A NAIL.DO NOT USE AS A MIRROR ADHESIVE: USE EVERBUILD MIRRORMATE DO NOT USE ON POLYSTYRENE/STYROFOAM/EXPANDED POLYURETHANE - USE EVERBUILD GUN A NAIL.HEA
VY MATERIALS (GREATER THAN 8KG PER SQ METER) MUST BE SUPPORTED FOR AT LEAST 8-24 HOURS DEPENDING ON SIZE OF ITEM.  SOLVENTS PRESENT MAY ATTACK SENSITIVE PLASTICS. IF IN DOUBT, REST A SMALL AREA FIRST.  C4: 350ML.

name: EVERBUILD 115 GENERAL PURPOSE BUILDING MASTIC
description:
Everbuild EVERFLEX 115 GP building mastic is an oil based compound intended for general pointing and sealing of many joints in traditional forms of construction. The sealant is rapidly and simply applied by extrusion from a cartridge gun. The product has good adhesion to most clean, dry surfaces.

BENEFITS
- Overpaintable.
- Adheres to most common surfaces.
- Semi drying - remains permanently plastic beneath surface skin.
- High solids formulation - excellent gap filling properties without shrinkage.
- Good external weathering properties.

AREAS FOR USE
- Perimeter pointing internally and externally around doors and windows.
- Adheres to concrete, brick, wood, metals and glass without the use of a primer.

name: MIRROR MATE SEALANT & ADHESIVE 290ML
description: EVERBUILD EVERFLEX MIRROR MATE IS A ONE PART, CHEMICALLY CURING SOLVENT-FREE SEALANT AND ADHESIVE COMBINING THE BEST QUALITIES OF SILICONE AND POLYURETHANE SEALANTS. IT IS SPECIFICALLY DESIGNED FOR ADHERING MOST COMMON MIRRORS TO ALL COMMON SUBSTRATES WITHOUT ATTACKING THE BACKING.  WHEN CURED, EVERBUILD MIRROR MATE CAN BE OVER PAINTED WITH MOST WATER AND GLOSS BASED PAINTS AND HAS SANITARY QUALITY WITH A COMBINED HIGHLY RESISTANT TO MILDEW AND MOULD GROWTH FORMULA. THE PRODUCT IS A JOY TO WORK WITH AS THE FAST CURING TIME IS IDEAL FOR THE APPLICATION, TACK FREE IN 10-MINUTES AND FULLY CURED IN 24-48 HOURS WITH EXCELLENT CHEMICAL RESISTANCE.  AREAS FOR USE:BONDING MIRRORS TO MOST COMMON SUBSTRATES.AUTOMOTIVE GAP FILLING AND SEALING.SEALING AND BONDING MARBLE AND GRANITE WHERE NON-STAINING IS ESSENTIAL. EXTERNAL AND INTERNAL PERIMETER POINTING AROUND DOORS AND WINDOWS, ESPECIALLY IN MOBILE STRUCTURES SUCH AS CARAVANS AND BOATS.SEALING VERTICAL EXPANSION JOINTS.JOINTING CLADDING PANELS.AS A HIGH QUALITY NAIL REPLACEMENT ADHESIVE, EVEN TO DAMP SURFACES.BONDING DIFFICULT MATERIALS SUCH AS SPECIALISED POLYMER SYSTEMS, METALS AND FIBREGLASS.ANY APPLICATION REQUIRING HIGH PERFORMANCE, DURABLE SEALING AND BONDING OF JOINTS.APPLICATIONS WHERE RESISTANCE TO CHEMICAL SPILLAGE IS REQUIRED (GARAGE FORECOURTS ETC.).

name: EVERBUILD MULTI-PURPOSE LINSEED OIL PUTTY
description:
Everbuild 101 Multi-Purpose Linseed Oil Putty is a hand-applied, setting glazing compound for sealing glass into metal and wooden frames.

Benefits:

- Easier to apply than most competitive putties.
- Extended shelf life.
- For wood and metal frames.
- Added plasticiser improves adhesion and helps prevent cracking.
- Single glazing of pretreated wooden and metal rebates.

Limitations:

- Unsuitable for plastic frames, heat-absorbing glass, double glazing or frames treated with decorative microporous stains.
- Always mix contents of pack thoroughly to blend in any surface oil.
- Do not overpaint until a surface skin has formed (minimum 7 days, maximum 30 days).

This Everbuild 101 Multi-Purpose Linseed Oil Putty comes in:

name: WET ROT WOOD HARDENER 250ML
description:
THE EVERBUILD BRAND IS NOT ONLY HUGELY POPULAR WITH TRADESMEN AND DIY'ERS. IT'S QUITE LITERALLY HUGE - THE BIGGEST RANGE IN THE BUSINESS. IN ADDITION TO CORE MANUFACTURED PRODUCTS THE EVERBUILD RANGE INCLUDES A WIDE RANGE OF ANCILLARY ITEMS FROM SEALANT GUNS TO DUST SHEETS, LINE MARKERS TO MASKING TAPE.  THE RANGE OF PRODUCTS EVERBUILD ACTUALLY MANUFACTURE IS EXTENSIVE, FROM CHEMICAL BLENDING FOR ADMIXTURES AND WATER PROOFERS THROUGH WATER BASED SEALANT MANUFACTURING TO THE HIGHLY ADVANCED POLYMER ENGINEERING UNDERTAKEN IN MANUFACTURING SILICONE AND HYBRID SEALANTS, AS WELL AS ADHESIVES AND A WIDE RANGE OF POWDER PRODUCTS.  EVERBUILD WET ROT WOOD HARDENER IS A HIGHLY PENETRATIVE SOLUTION OF SELECTED RESINS IN SOLVENT WHICH SOAKS DEEP INTO THE FIBRES OF DECAYING WOOD AND DRIES TO LEAVE THE WOOD HARD AND RESISTANT TO FURTHER MOISTURE PENETRATION.  THE RESIN-MODIFIED WOOD THEN BECOMES AN IDEAL BASE FOR REPAIR WITH HIGH PERFORMANCE WOOD FILLER. THE WET ROT WOOD HARDENER SOLUTION IS DRY IN 6 HOURS AND IS SUITABLE FOR INTERIOR AND EXTERIOR USE PROVIDING A COST-EFFECTIVE ALTERNATIVE TO REPLACING JOINERY AFFECTED BY WET ROT.  WET ROT WOOD HARDENER BINDS TOGETHER DAMAGED WOOD TO FORM A SOLID BASE FOR FILLING AND REDUCES SUBSEQUENT WATER PENETRATION. IT IS SUITABLE FOR REPAIRING WOOD DAMAGED BY WET ROT AND FOR STRENGTHENING, REINFORCING AND SEALING BOTH SOFTWOOD AND HARDWOOD PRIOR TO PAINTING.  SPECIFICATION  SIZE: 250 ML.ACTIVITY: 25&PLUSMN; 1% W/W.DRYING TIME: 6 HOURS.SPECIFIC GRAVITY: CA. 0.9.FLASH POINT: -17&DEG;C.BASE: ORGANIC RESIN IN ACETONE/SOLVENT BLEND.CONSIST
ENCY: WATER THIN CLEAR/OPAQUE SOLUTION.

name: FLEXIBLE DRIVE SHAFT 1.1M 6MM CAPACITY
description: A 1.1M (43IN) LONG FLEXIBLE DRIVE SHAFT THAT WILL FIT DIRECTLY INTO THE CHUCK OF ANY CORDLESS OR ELECTRIC POWER DRILL.  THE REINFORCED ENDS AND ANTI-KINK DESIGN PREVENTS WEAR AND HELPS PROVIDE A LONG WORKING LIFE.  A 6MM (1/4IN) CAPACITY KEYLESS CHUCK MAKES CHANGING BITS EASY AND THE PLASTIC HAND GRIP PROVIDES A FIRM HOLD MAKING THE SHAFT EASY TO GUIDE WHEN IN USE.  USING A FLEXIBLE DRIVE ENABLES YOU TO TAKE YOUR POWER TOOL TO THE MOST INACCESSIBLE PLACES.  IT MAY BE USED WITH DRILL BITS, WIRE BRUSHES, COUNTERSINKS, FLAP WHEELS, MOUNTED STONES AND GRINDING WHEELS.  PLEASE NOTE: - THE 6MM SHANK IS NOT HEX AS DESCRIBED ON THE PACKAGING IT IS ROUND.

name: HEAVY-DUTY FOAM GUN (FULL NON STICK BODY)
description: FAITHFULL HEAVY-DUTY FOAM GUN (FULL NON STICK BODY) IS A HIGH QUALITY PROFESSIONAL FOAM (SPURT) GUN DESIGNED FOR USE WITH STANDARD 500ML AND 750ML GUN GRADE POLYURETHANE PRESSURISED EXPANDING FOAM CANISTERS.  THE FEATURES OF THIS GUN INCLUDE A SPRUNG TRIGGER MECHANISM AND MICRO-FAST FOAM FLOW ADJUSTMENT SYSTEM ALLOWING THE USER FINE CONTROL OVER THE FOAM OUTPUT, TO PROVIDE A CLEAN EVEN BEAD FOR THE ACCURATE INSTALLATION OF THE FOAM AND TO HELP REDUCE WASTE. THE BARREL IS HERMETICALLY SEALED ONCE THE TRIGGER HAS BEEN RELEASED TO PREVENT THE HARDENING OF THE FOAM WHEN LEFT IN THE GUN.  ADDITIONAL FEATURES INCLUDE A FULLY COATED NON-STICK BODY, A NON-STICK COATED NEEDLE AND CANISTER FITTING VALVE AND A STAINLESS STEEL BARREL TO HELP MAKE CLEANING THE GUN EASIER.  THE GUN IS SUPPLIED COMPLETE WITH TWO TYPES OF ADDITIONAL PLASTIC EXTENSION BARRELS TO GIVE BETTER ACCESS WHEN USED IN CERTAIN APPLICATIONS;  2 X LONG PLASTIC EXTENSION BARRELS.2 X SHORT PLASTIC NARROW ACCESS BARRELS.  APPLICATIONS INCLUDE THE INSTALLATION OF DOOR AND WINDOW FRAMES, FILLING AND SEALING OF CAVITIES AND JOINTS, PIPE OR CABLE PENETRATIONS IN WALLS AND THE SEALING OF JOINTS IN WALL INSULATION SHEETS.

THE GUN HAS A SPRUNG TRIGGER MECHANISM AND FLOW ADJUSTER KNOB TO ENSURE FINE CONTROL OVER THE FOAM OUTPUT, AND TO PROVIDE A CLEAN, EVEN BEAD FOR THE ACCURATE INSTALLATION OF THE FOAM WHICH HELPS TO REDUCE WASTE. IT IS SUPPLIED COMPLETE WITH TWO TYPES OF ADDITIONAL PLASTIC EXTENSION BARRELS TO GIVE BETTER ACCESS WHEN USED IN CERTAIN APPLICATIONS.  IDEAL FOR THE FOLLOWING APPLICATIONS:INSTALLATION OF DOOR AND WINDOW FRAMES.FILLING AND SEALING OF CAVITIES AND JOINTS.PIPE OR CABLE PENETRATIONS IN WALLS.SEALING JOINTS IN WALL INSULATION SHEETS. name: SDS PLUS CIRCULAR CUTTER
description: FAITHFULL ELECTRICAL BACK BOX CUTTERS ARE A LABOUR AND TIME SAVING SYSTEM, DESIGNED TO CUT SOCKETS IN BLOCKWORK AND BRICK WALLS FOR THE SITING OF ELECTRICAL BACK BOXES. THEY ARE USED IN CONJUNCTION WITH LIGHTWEIGHT 2KG SDS FIXING HAMMERS WITH A ROTATION STOP FUNCTION.  THIS TCT CUTTER BIT IS DESIGNED FOR USE WITH FAITHFULL BOX CUTTERS TO FORM RECESSES FOR EITHER SINGLE OR DOUBLE ELECTRICAL BACK BOXES. IT CUTS 77MM ROUND HOLES IN BLOCK, SOFT BRICK AND CONCRETE. THE CUTTER HAS PRECISION MACHINED CUTTING EDGES AND IS DESIGNED FOR USE WITH 2KG SDS PLUS ROTARY HAMMER DRILLS.  CUTTER BIT SIZE: 77MM  SET INCLUDES:1 X SDS PLUS SHANK DRILL 8 X 160MM.1 X SDS PLUS FLAT CHISEL 20 X 140MM.  USE IN CONJUNCTION WITH FAISDSBOXSML AND FAISDSBOXLRG BOX CUTTERS TO FORM RECESSES FOR ELECTRICAL BACK BOXES.

name: FAITHFULL DIAMOND CERAMIC MINI HOLESAW
description:
The Faithfull Diamond Ceramic Mini Holesaws have a tough braze bonded diamond edge and durable alloy body, this gives these holesaws an extremely long lifespan. The round shank is suitable for use with cordless power drills only.

Ideal for tough drilling situations, they cut holes fast and cleanly. Easy to start, with no guide drill required. They will easily cut through porcelain tile, ceramic tile, granite, marble, slate, glass, cast iron, brick/block (lightweight), plasterboard, cement board, fibreglass, carbon fibre, composites and stucco.

Minimal water cooling is needed, simply dip in water before starting cut. At full RPM, start drilling at a 45 angle to the tile, raise to 90 and oscillate during cutting. Dip in water every 5 seconds during cutting for optimal life.

name: HAND DIY TILE CUTTER TCT TIPPED
description: A FAITHFULL EASY TO USE TILE SCRIBE FITTED WITH A TUNGSTEN CARBIDE TIPPED BLADE THAT WILL PROVIDE A LONG WORKING LIFE. THE SCRIBE IS SUITABLE FOR SCORING CERAMIC WALL AND FLOOR TILES PRIOR TO SNAPPING TO SIZE AND FEATURES A CONTOURED HANDLE THAT PROVIDES A FIRM GRIP AND HELPS MAINTAIN THE CORRECT BLADE ANGLE WHEN SCRIBING.  HOW TO USE:MARK THE TILE TO BE CUT AND PLACE IT FACE UP ON A SOLID SURFACE. PLACE A STEEL RULE ON THE TILE AND LINE THE ENDS UP WITH YOUR CUT MARKS. DRAW THE TILE SCRIBE FIRMLY ALONG THE RULE TO SCORE THE TILE. THICK TILES MAY NEED EXTRA ATTENTION AT THE EDGES, SCORE THESE INDEPENDENTLY IF REQUIRED. PLACE THE SCORED TILE ON TO A FLAT SURFACE WITH A PIECE OF THIN WIRE DIRECTLY UNDERNEATH THE SCORED LINE AND LINE UP THE WIRE WITH THE SCORE MARK AT THE TOP AND BOTTOM OF THE TILE. ONCE POSITIONED CORRECTLY, APPLY PRESSURE TO BOTH EDGES OF THE TILE AT THE SAME TIME TO SNAP THE TILE.

name: SCOURING PAD HOLDER + FINE MEDIUM & COARSE PADS
description:
THIS HANDY FAITHFULL KIT CONTAINS ALL THE ESSENTIAL COMPONENTS REQUIRED TO REMOVE EXCESS GROUT FROM TILED SURFACES QUICKLY AND EASY AFTER GROUTING IS COMPLETED.  CONTENTS: 1 X SCOURING PAD HOLDER.1 X WHITE (FINE) NYLON PAD.1 X BROWN (MEDIUM) NYLON PAD.1 X BLACK (COARSE) NYLON PAD.  THE TROWEL (SCOURING PAD HOLDER) IS COMFORTABLE TO USE AND FITTED WITH A HOOK AND LOOP FIXING SYSTEM, THAT PROVIDES A LARGE FLAT WORKING SURFACE FOR THE RAPID REMOVAL OF GROUT AND FOR FINAL POLISHING OF TILED SURFACES.  NYLON PADS MAY ALSO BE USED FOR MANY CLEANING APPLICATIONS AROUND THE HOME. THE THREE GRADES OF PADS SUPPLIED PROVIDE ADDED VERSATILITY FOR BOTH TILING AND CLEANING TASKS. FOR BEST RESULTS ALWAYS USE WET WITH WATER OR THE SELECTED CLEANING FLUID.  PAD SIZE APPROX. 250 X 120 X 20MM  WHITE &NDASH; FINE: A NON-ABRASIVE PAD FOR HIGH GLOSS POLISHING OR LIGHT CLEAN UP JOBS ON STONE OR TILED SURFACES. EXCELLENT FOR THE REMOVAL OF GREASE AND SOAP SCUM, WHEN USED WITH A MILD CLEANER OR DETERGENT. THIS PAD CAN ALSO BE USED FOR OBTAINING A HIGH GLOSS POLISHED FINISH. THE OPEN TEXTURE ALLOWS FOR A SMOOTH EVEN FINISH.  BROWN &NDASH; MEDIUM: A GENERAL PURPOSE ABRASIVE PAD FOR MOST CLEANING AND FINISHING REQUIREMENTS, EXCELLENT FOR CLEANING OR SURFACE PREPARATION. REMOVES FINE GROUT HAZE AND GROUT FROM TILED OR STONE SURFACES AND MAY BE USED WITH MOST SOLVENTS.  BLACK &NDASH; COARSE: A HEAVY-DUTY ABRASIVE PAD FOR THE INITIAL CLEANING OF NEWLY TILED AREAS AND FOR THE REMOVAL OF EXCESS GROUT. USE WITH HEAVY-DUTY CLEANERS FOR BEST RESULTS. OPEN MESH TEXTURE CAN MINI
MISE THE LOADING OF LIQUIDS EFFICIENTLY AND MAKE IT EASY TO WASH OUT AFTER USE.
categories: TOOLS/DECORATING & WOOD CARE/TILING TOOLS & TILE ADHESIVES

name: GROUT SCRUBBING BRUSH SOFT-GRIP HANDLE
description: THE FAITHFULL HEAVY-DUTY NARROW-HEADED GROUT SCRUBBING BRUSH IS FITTED WITH STIFF NYLON BRISTLES AND IS SUITABLE FOR USE ON ALL TILED SURFACES. IT IS IDEAL FOR TACKLING STUBBORN GRIME, MILDEW AND OTHER FORMS OF RESIDUE IN HARD TO REACH PLACES AND TIGHT GROUT LINES.A LARGE SOFT GRIP HANDLE PROVIDES EXTRA USER COMFORT. IT MAY BE USED IN CONJUNCTION WITH MOST TILE AND GROUT CLEANING DETERGENT.HOW TO USE: THOROUGHLY CLEAN THE TILED AREA WITH A SUITABLE CLEANER AND ALLOW TO DRY. SPRAY THE GROUT WITH A GROUT CLEANER AND ALLOW 3 TO 5 MINUTES TO PENETRATE, BUT DO NOT ALLOW TO DRY. USE THE SPECIAL NARROW BRUSH HEAD TO TRACK THE GROOVE ALLOWING MAXIMUM BRISTLE CONTACT WITH THE GROUT. WIPE CLEAN WITH A DAMP CLOTH TO ENSURE THAT NO DIRT IS WASHED BACK OVER INTO THE GROUT GROOVES. FOR BEST RESULTS POLISH WITH A DRY CLOTH.
categories: TOOLS/DECORATING & WOOD CARE/TILING TOOLS & TILE ADHESIVES

name: SILICONE SCRAPER KIT TWO PIECE
description: THIS FAITHFULL SILICONE REMOVER AND FINISHING KIT CONTAINS ALL THE COMPONENTS NEEDED TO ACHIEVE A PROFESSIONAL LOOKING FINISH TO SILICONE AND GROUT.  THIS ALL-IN-ONE TOOL IS QUICK, CLEAN AND SIMPLE TO USE WITH A CHOICE OF FIVE 'EASY CHANGE' FINISHING PROFILE RADIUSES. THE FINISHING TOOL ALSO FEATURES A SILICONE REMOVER, A NOZZLE AND OUTLET CUTTER, ALONG WITH A DETAIL TIP AND FLAT SURFACE CLEANING BLADE.  AFTER USE, SIMPLY WIPE THE TOOLS CLEAN AND PEEL OFF THE WASTE READY FOR THE NEXT JOB.

description: THIS FAITHFULL SILICONE SEALANT REMOVAL KNIFE HAS BEEN SPECIALLY DESIGNED TO REMOVE OLD SILICONE AND ACRYLIC JOINTS FROM A VARIETY OF SURFACES WITHOUT DAMAGING THE UNDERLYING STRUCTURE. name: MODULAR COMPACT BACKPACK 30CM (11.5IN)
description: THIS FACOM BACKPACK IS COMPACT, LIGHTWEIGHT AND DESIGNED FOR USE IN TIGHT AREAS, INCLUDING ON SAFETY LADDERS. MADE FROM DURABLE BALLISTIC NYLON FABRIC (1680 DENIER), THIS ROBUST BAG IS ABRASION AND WATER RESISTANT. ITS TPR FEET ARE DESIGNED TO PREVENT DAMAGE FROM ROUGH SURFACES.  THE BACKPACK HAS PADDED SHOULDER STRAPS WITH QUICK-RELEASE MECHANISM TO PROVIDE EXTRA SAFETY WHILST ENSURING MAXIMUM CARRYING COMFORT AND OPTIMUM LOAD DISTRIBUTION. A QUICK-GRAB HANDLE PROVIDES AN ADDITIONAL CARRYING OPTION. THE 100% OPENING FLAP ALLOWS EASY ACCESS TO TOOLS, EVEN ON THE MOVE.  THE BAG HAS NUMEROUS FEATURES FOR EXCELLENT ORGANISATION:INTERNAL D-RINGS AND EXTERNAL ROUND HOOPS WHICH ARE COMPATIBLE WITH SLS TOOLS.OVAL OUTER EYELETS WHICH CAN CARRY UP TO 0.5KG EACH.SMART INNER ORGANISATION WITH FASTENING FLAPS.4 HOOK AND LOOP REMOVABLE POCKETS.TRANSPARENT REMOVABLE DOCUMENT/TABLET POUCH.REMOVABLE ORGANISER.EXTERNAL STRETCH SIDE POCKET

name: JET.5M3 5 DRAWER ROLLER CABINET RED
description: THE FACOM JET.5M3 CABINET IS FINISHED IN A DURABLE, EPOXY RED PAINT. IT HAS HIGH QUALITY, SOFT FEEL PROTECTIVE BUMPERS WITH DAMPER EFFECT TO ABSORB SHOCK. ITS ROBUST RECESSED FOLDING KEY AND CENTRAL LOCKING SYSTEM PROVIDE EXCELLENT TOOL SECURITY AND ITS LARGE DIAMETER WHEELS ENSURE EASY MANOEUVRABILITY AND REDUCED RISK OF OVERTURNING.  THE CABINET'S 100% DRAWER OPENING SYSTEM ALLOWS COMPLETE ACCESS TO TOOLS AND FREEDOM OF ARRANGEMENT. IN ADDITION, THESE DRAWERS ARE COMPATIBLE WITH THE FACOM TOOL CONTROL STORAGE MODULES.  THIS 5 DRAWER ROLLER CABINET COMPRISES THE FOLLOWING DRAWERS:  2 X 60MM HIGH DRAWERS.2 X 130MM HIGH DRAWERS.1 X 270MM HIGH DRAWER.  EACH OF THE 60MM AND 130MM DRAWERS HAS THE CAPACITY TO HOLD 3 MODULES EACH. THE CABINET IS SUPPLIED WITH 4 PARTITIONS FOR THE 60MM DRAWERS AND 4 PARTITIONS FOR THE 130MM DRAWERS.  SPECIFICATIONS:  MAX LOAD PER DRAWER: 125KG.STORAGE VOLUME: 155 LITRES.WEIGHT: 73.5KG.

name: JET 6 HEAVY-DUTY MOBILE WORKBENCH
description: THE FACOM JET 6 HEAVY-DUTY MOBILE WORKBENCH IS FITTED WITH A LARGE, 0.7M&SUP2;, STRONG WORKTOP IN MULTI LAYERED BEECH WOOD, THAT IS COATED WITH LINT OIL FOR A STRONGER RESISTANCE TO LIQUIDS AND EASIER MAINTENANCE. THE FEET CAN BE RAISED VIA A ROTATING HANDLE TO MAKE YOUR WORKBENCH AS STABLE AS A FIXED WORKBENCH, STATIC RESISTANCE IS 1-TON ON THE FEET AND 500KG ON WHEELS. LOWER THE FEET VIA THE ROTATING HANDLE AND THE WORKBENCH IS MOBILE AGAIN.  IT OFFERS HIGH CAPACITY STORAGE WITH 6 DRAWERS THAT ARE COMPATIBLE WITH XL MODULES, ALUMINIUM HANDLES AND WITHSTANDING A LOAD OF 30KG PER DRAWER. THERE IS ALSO 1 LARGE LATERAL COMPARTMENT TO STORE LARGER TOOLS OR OBJECTS, AND A SINGLE KEY FOR THE DRAWERS AND COMPARTMENT.  THE LEFT-HAND SIDE AND BACK OF THE WORKBENCH CAN STORE THE JETXL ACCESSORIES AND THE WORKTOP IS PERFORATED FOR EASY INSTALLATION OF A JET.A6M5 PERFORATED PANEL. IT HAS 4 X 125MM DIAMETER WHEELS, 2 SWIVELLING AND 2 FIXED.  SPECIFICATION  DIMENSIONS (LXDXH) 1194 X 670 X 1002MM.WEIGHT: 127.8KG.

name: JET.7M3 ROLLER CABINET 7 DRAWER RED
description: THE FACOM JET+3 TOOL STORAGE SOLUTIONS ARE DESIGNED TO FIT 3 FACOM MODULES PER DRAWER.  THE DRAWER HANDLES ARE MADE FROM ANTI-OXIDATION ANODIZED ALUMINUM. THE DRAWERS OPEN 100% AND ARE SHOT BLASTED FOR LONG LIFE. THE WORKTOP HAS A BUILT-IN HANDLE AND SLOTS FOR 16 SCREWDRIVERS.  THE CABINET HAS SOFT BUMPERS MADE FROM ELASTOMERIC PLASTIC, WHICH HELP TO DAMPEN SHOCK ON ITS 4 EDGES. THIS PLASTIC IS ALSO FOUND ON THE DRAWERS, PROTECTING THEIR ALUMINUM HOOKS. THE HIGH-PERFORMANCE WHEELS MAKE THE CABINET EASY TO HANDLE, HAVE A LONG LIFETIME AND OFFER A HIGH RESISTANCE TO HEAVY LOADS.  THE CABINET HAS THE FOLLOWING DRAWERS, EACH HOLDING 3 MODULES: 5 X 60MM HIGH DRAWERS.1 X 130MM HIGH DRAWER.1 X 200MM HIGH DRAWER.  SUPPLIED WITH 6 PARTITIONS FOR 60MM DRAWERS AND 2 PARTITIONS FOR 130MM DRAWER.  TOTAL LOAD ACCEPTABLE IN THE DRAWERS: 155KG.USEFUL STORAGE VOLUME: 155 LITRES.OVERALL SIZE: 97.1 X 77.4 X 54.6CMWEIGHT: 77.5 KG.

name: HEAVY-DUTY DOOR BOLT - BRASS 150MM (6IN)
description: THIS FORGE DOOR BOLT IS HEAVY-DUTY AND YET STILL DECORATIVE. IT IS MADE FROM SOLID BRASS AND LAQUERED TO PREVENT DISCOLOURATION DURING USE.  IDEAL FOR INTERNAL DOORS AND FOR USE AS SECONDARY SECURITY.  SUPPLIED WITH SCREWS AND FITTING INSTRUCTIONS.  FITTING INSTRUCTIONS:1. name: CORDLESS LED BLUETOOTH SITE LIGHT 7.4V 20W 2300 LUMENS
description: THE FAITHFULL POWER PLUS CORDLESS SITE LIGHT PROVIDES A CONVENIENT PORTABLE 'LEAD FREE' LIGHT SOURCE TO ILLUMINATE YOUR WORKSITE. THE INTEGRATED BLUETOOTH® SPEAKER SYSTEM ALLOWS YOU TO LISTEN TO YOUR FAVOURITE MUSIC, VIA YOUR MOBILE PHONE, MP3 PLAYER OR TABLET. THE SITE LIGHT ALSO FEATURES A USB OUTLET 'POWERBANK' FUNCTION PERMITTING YOU TO RECHARGE PERSONAL ITEMS SUCH AS MOBILE PHONES, MP3 PLAYERS OR TABLETS USING A COMPATIBLE USB LEAD.  THE SITE LIGHT MAY BE USED IN CONJUNCTION WITH ITS TRIPOD STAND OR AS A FREE-STANDING POD LIGHT WHEN WORKING IN ENCLOSED SPACES, WITH NO NEED FOR A NEARBY POWER SOCKET OR TRAILING LEADS. IT HAS 3 LIGHT OUTPUT MODES: 10%, 50% OR 100%, EACH MODE OFFERS A DIFFERENT RUN TIME. THE LIGHT CAN STILL BE USED WHILST IT RECHARGES, RECHARGED IN 4 HOURS.  THIS TRULY PORTABLE SITE LIGHT CAN BE USED TO PROVIDE LIGHT AND SOUND JUST ABOUT ANYWHERE. LED SITE LIGHTS PROVIDE A HIGH LIGHT OUTPUT, A COOL RUNNING TEMPERATURE AND A LOW POWER CONSUMPTION, AND PROVIDE A LONG RUNNING TIME EVEN WHEN USED WITH BATTERIES. LEDS ARE MAINTENANCE FREE AND MORE RESILIENT TO IMPACT DAMAGE THAT CAN CAUSE CONVENTIONAL HALOGEN TUBES TO FAIL IF A LIGHT IS HIT OR KNOCKED OVER.  SUPPLIED WITH: 1 X 7.4V 4400MAH LI-ION BATTERY PACK, 1 X 12V 1A MAINS CHARGER & 1 X 12V CAR CHARGER  SPECIFICATION:  LUMENS: 2,300HEIGHT: UP TO 1,800MMRUN TIME (APPROX.): 10% 12 HOURS, 50% 6 HOURS, 100% 3 HOURS IP RATING: IP54

name: RECHARGEABLE SMD LED WORK LIGHT WITH MAGNETIC BASE 900 LUMENS 10W
description:
THE FAITHFULL POWER PLUS RECHARGEABLE SMD LED WORK LIGHT HAS BEEN DEVELOPED AND DESIGNED PRIMARILY FOR TRADESMEN TO USE ON THE WORKSITE OR INSIDE WHERE THERE MAY BE POOR LIGHTING, OR NO LIGHTING AT ALL. ONE OF ITS BIGGEST BENEFITS IS THAT IT IS COMPACT AND CAN BE EASILY STORED DURING TRANSIT, AND WON&RSQUO;T GET IN THE WAY DURING USE.  USING THE LATEST SMD LED TECHNOLOGY, THIS IS A ROBUST AND EXTREMELY POWERFUL 10W PORTABLE LIGHT WHICH PROVIDES USERS WITH AN INCREDIBLY BRIGHT, GLARE-FREE LIGHT. IT OFFERS 3 OUTPUT MODES FOR VERSATILITY AND EXTENDED RUNNING TIMES. CHOOSE FROM 100%, 50% AND 25%, PROVIDING 900, 450, OR 225 LUMENS OF LIGHT. UNLIKE MANY TRADITIONAL SITE LIGHTS, THIS ONE DOES NOT EMIT HEAT, SO THE GLASS IS COOL TO THE TOUCH. THAT&RSQUO;S NOT ONLY A GREAT SAFETY FEATURE, IT&RSQUO;S ALSO A MASSIVE BENEFIT TO TRADESMEN SUCH AS PLASTERERS WHERE THE HEAT FROM TRADITIONAL LIGHTS CAN DRY OUT THE PLASTER TOO QUICKLY AND CRACK IT.  ITS HEAVY-DUTY LITHIUM-ION BATTERY IS LIGHTWEIGHT BUT POWERFUL, PROVIDING FROM 3 TO 12 HOURS OF CONTINUOUS LIGHT ON ONE FULL CHARGE. THE POWER BANK USB PORT WILL ENABLE YOU TO CHARGE PERSONAL ITEMS SUCH AS MP3 PLAYERS AND EVEN MOBILE PHONES WITH A COMPATIBLE LEAD. THIS COULD PROVIDE EXTRA PEACE OF MIND WHEN WORKING IN REMOTE AREAS.  THE STURDY STEEL STAND IS FITTED WITH 4 POWERFUL MAGNETS AND AN ERGONOMICALLY DESIGNED MOULDED GRIP. THE HEAD CAN BE SET AT ANY ANGLE VIA THE FRICTION THUMB TURN KNOBS SO YOU CAN HAVE LIGHT EXACTLY WHERE YOU NEED IT.  IT IS SUPPLIED COMPLETE WITH BOTH A MAINS USB CH
ARGER AND A CAR CHARGER UNIT.  WEATHERPROOF TO IP65 STANDARD

name: G3613DB MULTIVOLT BRUSHLESS GRINDER 125MM 36/18V 2 X 2.5/5.0AH LI-ION
description: THE HIKOKI G3613DB MULTIVOLT BRUSHLESS GRINDER WITH A LARGE 2-STAGE PADDLE SWITCH (DEAD MAN ACTION). FITTED WITH A BRUSHLESS MOTOR FOR INCREASED POWER AND PERFORMANCE THANKS TO THE IMPROVED ELECTRICAL EFFICIENCY AND POWER TRANSFER. IT HAS A LIGHTWEIGHT AND COMPACT BODY WITH A DUST AND WATER-RESISTANT CONSTRUCTION.  5-STAGE VARIABLE SPEED SYSTEM PLUS AUTO MODE: THE SPEED AUTOMATICALLY SHIFTS BETWEEN HIGH (9,500/MIN.) AND LOW (5,500/MIN.) SPEEDS DEPENDING ON THE LOAD, RESULTING IN MORE EFFECTIVE OPERATION. THIS MACHINE IS PACKED FULL OF SAFETY FEATURES: AN ELECTRONIC BRAKE, KICKBACK PROTECTION SYSTEM, ANTI-RESTART PROTECTION AND SOFT START.  THIS MACHINE UTILISES THE NEXT GENERATION OF 36V BATTERY POWER DEVELOPED FROM USER NEEDS AND HIKOKI'S ORIGINAL TECHNOLOGY. BATTERIES ARE COMPATIBLE WITH EXISTING HITACHI 18V TOOLS.  SUPPLIED WITH: 2 X 36/18V 2.5/5.0AH LI-ION BATTERIES, 1 X SIDE HANDLE, 1 X WRENCH, 1 X ABRASIVE WHEEL, 1 X UC18YSL3 CHARGER AND 1 X CARRY CASE  SPECIFICATION:  NO LOAD SPEED: 3,000 - 9,500/MIN.DISC DIAMETER: 125MM, M14 SPINDLEOVERALL LENGTH: 358MMWEIGHT: 2.8KG

name: NR1890DBCL BRUSHLESS FRAMING NAILER 18V 2 X 5.0AH LI-ION
description: THE HIKOKI NR1890DBCL CORDLESS FRAMING NAILER WITH A BRUSHLESS MOTOR FOR A LONGER RUN TIME, LESS MAINTENANCE AND INCREASED DURABILITY. NO AIR HOSE OR COMPRESSOR REQUIRED. ELIMINATES THE COST OF FUEL CELLS. AIR/SPRING DRIVE SYSTEM MEANS LESS RECOIL, BETTER FLUSH DRIVING AND EASIER MAINTENANCE.  FITTED WITH A SELECTIVE ACTIVATION BUTTON; EASILY CHOOSE BETWEEN SEQUENTIAL OR BUMP FIRE MODE. ALSO FEATURES TOOL-FREE ADJUSTMENT OF DRIVE DEPTH, A LOCK SWITCH AND 30 MINUTE AUTOMATIC SHUTDOWN FOR INCREASED SAFETY AND LONGER BATTERY LIFE. THE DRY FIRE LOCKOUT SYSTEM PREVENTS NAILER FROM DRIVING WHEN FASTENERS ARE LOW.  OTHER FEATURES INCLUDE A LOW BATTERY INDICATOR AND PIVOTING RAFTER HOOK.  SUPPLIED WITH: 2 X 18V 5.0AH LI-ION BATTERIES, 1 X CHARGER, 1 X SAFETY GLASSES, 1 X HEX WRENCH AND 1 X CASE  SPECIFICATION:  NAIL WIDTH: 2.9-3.3MMNAIL LENGTH: 50-90MMNAIL CAPACITY: 47 NAILSDRIVING SPEED: UP TO 2 NAILS/SEC.DIMENSIONS (LXWXH): 342 X 127 X 309MMWEIGHT: 4.5KG

name: NR90GC2 GAS CLIPPED HEAD STRIP FRAMING NAILER 7.2V 2 X 1.4AH LI-ION
description: THE HIKOKI NR90GC2 GAS CLIPPED HEAD STRIP FRAMING NAILER FIRES UP TO 1,200 NAILS PER FUEL CELL AND HAS A HIGH DRIVING POWER OF 90 JOULES. IT IS FITTED WITH A QUICK LOAD REAR ACCESS MAGAZINE AND A 2-ACTION NAIL FEED; SIMPLY DROP IN THE NAILS AND PULL BACK THE FEEDER. THE MAGAZINE DESIGN PROVIDES HIGH VISIBILITY AND LETS THE USER KNOW WHEN THEY'RE RUNNING LOW. THE DRY FIRING LOCKOUT FUNCTION PROVIDES INCREASED SAFETY AND PREVENTS A MISFIRE.  OTHER FEATURES INCLUDE A FOLD AWAY HOOK THAT FITS OVER JOISTS FOR GREATER CONVENIENCE, A LIGHTWEIGHT, WELL BALANCED DESIGN, LONGER TRIGGER STROKE FOR SAFER USE AND A NON-SLIP SOFT RUBBER GRIP. THE NAILER IS EASY TO CLEAN AND THERE IS EASY ACCESS TO THE FUEL CELL CHAMBER.  SUPPLIED WITH: 2 X 7.2V 1.4AH LI-ION BATTERIES, 1 X 1 HOUR CHARGER, 1 X PAIR OF SAFETY GLASSES, 1 X HEX WRENCH, 1 X CARRYING CASE.  PLEASE NOTE: ONLY PLAIN, BARBED AND RING NAILS CAN BE USED. THE USE OF ANY OTHER TYPE OF NAIL CAN RESULT IN TOOL MALFUNCTION.  SPECIFICATION:  NAILS: CLIPPED HEAD, PAPER COLLATED, 34&DEG; ANGLEMAX. MAGAZINE CAPACITY: 25-37 NAILSNAIL LENGTH RANGE: 50-90MMNAIL DIAMETER RANGE: 2.9-3.3MMWEIGHT: 3.5KG

name: NT65GS CORDLESS SECOND FIX FINISH NAILER 3.6V 2 X 1.5AH LI-ION
description: THE HIKOKI NT65GS CORDLESS SECOND FIX FINISH NAILER HAS A LIGHTWEIGHT COMPACT DESIGN AND CAN FIRE UP TO 1,200 NAILS PER FUEL CELL. THE GUN HAS BOTH TOOL-FREE DEPTH ADJUSTMENT AND JAM CLEARANCE, MAKING IT EASY TO CLEAN AND ADJUST WITHOUT ADDITIONAL TOOLS. IT IS ALSO HAS A DRY FIRING LOCKOUT FEATURE TO PREVENT THE GUN FROM FIRING WITHOUT NAILS IN THE MAGAZINE. IT IS FITTED WITH A HANDY BELT HOOK AND A NO MARK NOSE CAP INCLUDED. THE GUN WILL TAKE THE SAME NAILS AND GAS AS THE PASLODE IM65 NAIL GUN, ALLOWING YOU TO USE EXISTING STOCK AS WELL AS THE NEW HIKOKI NAILS. SUPPLIED WITH: 2 X 3.6V 1.5AH LI-ION BATTERIES, 1 X UC3SML 60 MINUTE CHARGER, 1 X SAFETY GLASSES, 2 X HEX WRENCHES, 1 X OIL, 1 X NOSE CAP, 1 X CARRYING CASE, 1 X INSTRUCTIONS. SPECIFICATION: MAX. name: 3-IN-ONE OIL AEROSOL CAN 200ML
description: 3-IN-ONE ORIGINAL SPRAY OIL PROVIDES A SPECIALLY FORMULATED LUBRICANT IN A CONVENIENT AEROSOL CAN. IT CLEANS AS WELL AS PROTECTING SURFACES FROM RUST AND CORROSION. IT CAN BE USED TO CLEAN METAL, LUBRICATE MOVING PARTS OR STOP SQUEAKS.

name: 3-IN-ONE AEROSOL WITH PTFE 250ML
description: 3-IN-ONE MULTI-PURPOSE OIL AEROSOL WITH PTFE IS A SUPERIOR LUBRICANT THAT OFFERS LONG LASTING PROTECTION. IDEAL FOR CHAINS, CABLES AND GEAR MECHANISMS.  SIZE: 250ML.

name: 3-IN-ONE PENETRANT SPRAY 400ML
description: 3-IN-ONE PENETRANT SPRAY HAS A FAST ACTING FORMULA, FREES RUSTED OR SEIZED FITTINGS. A MUST FOR THE TOOLBOX KIT FOR ANYONE WORKING WITH METAL FITTINGS AND COMPONENTS, PIPE WORK OR ENGINES. ITS FORMULA PENETRATES DEEPLY AND HELPS TO FREE OFF STUCK OR SEIZED NUTS, BOLTS AND FIXINGS.  SIZE: 400ML.

name: 3-IN-ONE SILICONE SPRAY 400ML
description: 3-IN-ONE SILICONE SPRAY PROVIDES HIGH-PERFORMANCE LUBRICATION AND CORROSION PROTECTION, IN A QUICK-DRYING NO-MESS FORMULA. ITS ADVANCED SILICONE SYNTHETIC FORMULA IS SAFE FOR USE ON METAL, RUBBER, WOOD, AND VINYL. IT ALSO PROTECTS ELECTRICAL PARTS AND IS PERFECT FOR WET ENVIRONMENTS AND MARINE USE.  NSF H2 REGISTERED, SAFE FOR USE IN FOOD-RELATED ENVIRONMENTS.

name: 3-IN-ONE WHITE LITHIUM SPRAY GREASE 400ML
description: 3-IN-ONE WHITE LITHIUM SPRAY GREASE HAS A WATER AND HEAT RESISTANT FORMULATION THAT PROVIDES YOU WITH A LONG-LASTING, HEAVY-DUTY LUBRICANT IN AN AEROSOL CAN. IT REDUCES FRICTION WHILE PROTECTING AGAINST RUST AND CORROSION. IT SPRAYS ON EVENLY AS A LIQUID, AND SETS UP DRY FOR A THICK COATING. IT WILL NOT SPLATTER, MELT, RUN, WASH OFF OR FREEZE.

name: 3-IN-ONE HIGH-PERFORMANCE LUBRICANT WITH PTFE 400ML
description: 3-IN-ONE HIGH PERFORMANCE LUBRICANT IS AN ADVANCED PTFE SYNTHETIC FLOUROPOLYMER FORMULA WHICH PROVIDES OUTSTANDING LUBRICATION AND CORROSION PROTECTION UNDER EXTREME TEMPERATURE, PRESSURE AND MOTION. FRICTION AND WEAR IS DRAMATICALLY REDUCED ON ALL MOVING PARTS WHICH ALSO EXTENDS THE LIFE OF TOOLS AND MACHINERY. SUITABLE FOR USE ON ALL METAL AND NON-METAL SURFACES INCLUDING WOOD, GLASS, VINYL, RUBBER AND PLASTICS (EXCEPT POLYCARBONATE AND POLYSTYRENE). THIS HIGH PERFORMANCE LUBRICANT WILL ALSO DRIVE OUT MOISTURE AND IS CAPABLE OF WITHSTANDING EXTREME TEMPERATURE FROM -45 &DEG; TO +235 &DEG; C.  SIZE 400ML SPRAY CAN

name: 3-IN-ONE HEAVY-DUTY CLEANER DEGREASER 500ML
description: 3-IN-ONE HEAVY-DUTY CLEANER DEGREASER HAS A DEEP PENETRATING CITRUS FOAMING ACTION THAT QUICKLY REMOVES GREASE, OIL, DIRT AND GRIME FROM ENGINES, TOOLS AND EQUIPMENT.   WORKS GREAT ON LAWNMOWERS, CHAINSAWS, POWER EQUIPMENT, AUTOMOTIVE AND TRUCK ENGINES AND PARTS, AS WELL AS GEARS, CHAINS, PULLEYS AND INDUSTRIAL MACHINERY.

name: 3-IN-ONE ANTI-SEIZE COPPER GREASE 300ML
description: 3-IN-ONE ANTI-SEIZE COPPER GREASE IS A HIGH-TEMPERATURE LUBRICANT AND ANTI-SEIZE COMPOUND THAT PROTECTS METAL COMPONENTS FROM CORROSION, RUST, WATER, HEAT AND ACID. CAPABLE OF WITHSTANDING EXTREME TEMPERATURES, THIS GREASE IS ALSO ENHANCED WITH GRAPHITE FOR EVEN BETTER LUBRICATION ACROSS THE ENTIRE TEMPERATURE RANGE. ONCE APPLIED, A PROTECTIVE COATING IS FORMED WHICH WILL NOT WASH OFF OR BURN, THEREFORE REDUCING METAL-TO-METAL FRICTION. ALSO ASSISTS WITH THE ASSEMBLY AND FUTURE DISMANTLING OF THREADED FASTENINGS.

name: 3.2 KW / 4.0 KVA GENERATOR KEY START
description:
THE HY3800LEK-2 IS A POWERFUL YET EASILY PORTABLE 3.2 KW / 4.0 KVA* OPEN FRAME GENERATOR FROM HYUNDAI. DESIGNED FOR BOTH HOME AND COMMERCIAL USE THE HY3800LEK-2 IS POWERED BY A 210 CC / 7.0 HP ECONOMICAL SINGLE CYLINDER HYUNDAI 4-STROKE ENGINE. THE INTEGRATED WHEEL KIT AND FOLDING HANDLE MAKE MOVING THIS MACHINE VERY EASY.  BUILT FOR THE MOST DEMANDING OF JOBS THE HY3800LEK-2 IS AN EXTREMELY RELIABLE GENERATOR, THE SINGLE CYLINDER 4-STROKE OHV AIR COOLED ENGINE GENERATES A MAXIMUM POWER OF 3.2 KW. WEIGHING ONLY 57 KG, THE HY3800LEK-2 HAS A RUGGED OPEN FRAME AND IS EASY TO MANOEUVRE THANKS TO ITS BUILT-IN WHEEL KIT, RUGGED OPEN FRAME AND FOLDING HANDLE.  THE HYUNDAI AVR ALTERNATOR KEEPS THE VOLTAGE OUTPUT SMOOTH, WITHIN &PLUSMN; 3% OF 230V. THIS MEANS IT CAN BE USED TO POWER SENSITIVE EQUIPMENT SUCH AS COMPUTERS, LAPTOPS AND CHARGE MOBILE PHONES. HOWEVER, THE AVR ALTERNATOR IS ALSO RUGGED ENOUGH TO HANDLE THE HARSH DEMANDS OF POWER TOOLS AND BUILDING SITE EQUIPMENT. THE HY3800LEK-2 IS AN ALL ROUND WORKHORSE. USING THE LATEST LOW NOISE ENGINE TECHNOLOGY, THE HY3800LEK-2 PRODUCES ONLY 65 DBA @ 7M.  THE EASY ELECTRIC KEY START FUNCTION MAKES STARTING THE GENERATOR SIMPLE. THERE IS ALSO A RECOIL START SYSTEM TO ENSURE YOU ARE NEVER LEFT WITHOUT POWER. THE GENERATOR RECHARGES ITS OWN BATTERY WHEN IN USE. FITTED WITH 1 X 230V 16A & 1 X 115V 16A SOCKET TO END FACING CONTROL PANEL, TO MINIMISE DAMAGE TO SOCKETS WHEN WHEELING GENERATOR THROUGH NARROW GAPS AND DOORWAYS. WITH LOW SERVICE AND MAINTENANCE REQUIREMENTS, THE HY3800LEK-2 IS INCREDIBLY USER-FRIENDLY,
 AND HAS FULL HYUNDAI UK PARTS BACK UP.  COVERED BY A HYUNDAI 3 YEAR PLATINUM WARRANTY (ON LINE REGISTRATION REQUIRED).  *KVA IS BASED ON AN ASSUMED LOAD FACTOR OF 0.8
